How to Find Flower
For a flower search app first we need to store different aspect and information about the flower in a database with the flower name tag, like colour, size, looks, originity, colour of leaf and pictures of a flower. Now the database should be connected with input field. If anyone search the flower by It's name the flower name will point that flower tag name field of the database and it will give output of that flower image, names and other information.
